  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and sauté until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Stir in minced garlic and red chili flakes, cooking for 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Add tomato paste and cook, stirring, for 1 minute.",
    "Pour in crushed tomatoes and vegetable broth, bring to a simmer.",
    "Add the penne pasta, stir gently, cover, and cook for 11-12 minutes until al dente.",
    "Reduce heat to low, then stir in ricotta and grated parmesan until melted and creamy.",
    "Fold in lemon zest and lemon juice, adjusting seasoning with salt and pepper.",
    "Top with chopped basil and serve hot.",
    "Enjoy the tangy, creamy goodness!"
  ],
